divs: Sighting Detailsi was driving home and saw two bright orange objects in the sky.what caught my eye was the brightness of the objects.the objects did not make any sound and were moving from west to east at a good rate of speed.the objects were round.they appeared to remain at the same elevation and disappeared as they moved eastward.
